title: BIP 6: Badger Grants Month 1
body:
Proposed by: Spadaboom

TLDR; Proposal to initiate grant process for rewarding contributors to BadgerDAO. 

Small change as we've added Poopster for Badger Support, added j.audefi for Grant Curator, and shifted Niklas to Internal Ops/PM as we've further finetuned needs and focused on skillsets. This results in a net change of 500 $BADGER from the original BIP 6 post.


---------------------------Past Contribution Grants---------------------------
- Jintao- He has created https://sett.vision/ the one stop dashboard for all things Badger. Grant 500 $BADGER
- vfat- He created https://vfat.tools/badger/ as an alternative for users to deposit in vaults and see their Badger position. This was critical when we had UI issues in the first couple days. Grant 500 $BADGER
